      "date": "2012-01-10 19:34:10.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/f4b8f384-3bc0-11e1-b20c-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
