          "tz": 480
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Hongchao Zhang",
          "email": "hongchao.zhang@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2012-01-10 12:31:43.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-969 debug: reduce stack usage",
        "message": "LU-969 debug: reduce stack usage\n\nvarious cases to reduce stack usage:\n - libcfs_debug_vmsg2 to accept libcfs_debug_msg_data structure\n   to replace SUBSYSTEM, __FILE__, __FUNCTION__, __LINE__ and cdls\n   on the stack\n - libcfs_debug_vmsg1 for regular users like CDEBUG() which don't\n   need 2 format strings\n - CDEBUG, CHECK_STACK, DEBUG_CAPA to use static libcfs_debug_msg_data\n - RETURN/GOTO use return code 3 times, libcfs_log_return and\n   libcfs_log_goto are introduced which accept return code once.\n - in ptlrpc_main, move struct lu_env to heap to save stack\n\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I33f700a8375abd8903d4902a1e0c2bd443026b7e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
